name: MyFundFinder.com
tag_list: hedge-fund, investor, capital-introduction, manager, service-provider, community
overview:
MyFundFinder is the meeting place for hedge funds and fund investors.

Discover a whole new way to search, match and connect with hedge funds, CTAs, and Funds of Funds. MyFundFinder gives you the tools to sucessfully navigate the dense data and quickly find funds that match your strict criteria.

Using an intuitive set of pulldowns, filters, and sliders, you can sort through over 1,900 Funds, Funds of Funds and CTAs to deliver a concise list that meets today’s stringent criteria and requirements - all from your desk!

Once you’ve discovered the funds available, you will be able to find a match.

Using a series of pulldowns and filters, adjust the ranges of your tolerances and provide specifics for the types of funds you’re looking for.

Drill down into your results for 121 data points on each fund - from benchmark comparison, to risk profiles, to biographies of principals. Add the fund to your personal watch list for review - or contact the manager directly, right from the page!
